text:
Alhamdulillah today i visited my client's place and had a chance to takeaway from the Muslim Food stall again.
I've been here few times - Muslim Food staffs are friendly, great. Makcik cooks delicious, clean food .. just like my mother 🥰. Service and atmosphere are pleasing too.

Sharing about the new mala store that opens here. Regarding all the other stores, will update slowly.

Spiciness is good and the taste for the meat and crabmeat really bland together with the Tau ki. Really sweet taste that revolve around your tongue. The below portion for $10.80, definitely not the cheapest out there but I believed for the taste, it's reasonable. Worth a try

Visited  15/10
The mixed vegetable rice is good.
Try the charsiew, it's 70% fat but very fragrant, no boar taint.

Good food at good prices with free parking!
Try the prawn soup mini pot. 👍👍👍
Plenty of food stalls here. You can choose from chinese food, indian food, malay food, etc... The place is okay and the price is quite reasonable. Thank you 🤗👌🏻
